#. type: delimited block =
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/foundations-data-quality.adoc:35
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/foundations-data-quality.adoc:48
msgid ""
"The two primary concepts that we will explore are Fitness for Use and "
"Measures of Quality.  These two ideas will lay the foundation for more "
"detailed data quality concepts and techniques in the future."
msgstr ""

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/foundations-data-quality.adoc:42
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/foundations-data-quality.adoc:55
msgid ""
"Photo: GBIF: https://www.gbif.org/occurrence/2550045989 Ictinaetus "
